room_title: Escape room "National Treasure" by Escape Room Cleveland in Cleveland
review: We had a group of all ages and did the National treasure room. it was a lot of fun, clean and entertaining. I've done quite a few escape rooms and this is definitely one of the best. I would highly recommend it.

room_title: Escape room "National Treasure" by Escape Room Cleveland in Cleveland
review: I just had the most amazing day ever!! me and a friend did the national treasure room and it was fun and challenging! to top the day off I threw an axe for the first time in my life and it was amazing. the employees are so nice and welcoming I'm definitely going back!! if there were more than 5 stars they would definitely have it!!!! Thank you guys for such a great experience:)

room_title: Escape room "National Treasure" by Escape Room Cleveland in Cleveland
review: Awesome experience! We did the National Treasure room and got out with less than a minute to spare! We will be back again!!!
